result:
<a-drawer
    :title="title"
    :width="800"
    placement="right"
    :closable="false"
    @close="close"
    :visible="visible"
>

  <a-spin :spinning="confirmLoading">
    <a-form :form="form">
    
      <a-form-item
        :labelCol="labelCol"
        :wrapperCol="wrapperCol"
        label="主键id">
        <a-input-number v-decorator="[ 'iId', validatorRules.iId ]" />
      </a-form-item>
      <a-form-item
        :labelCol="labelCol"
        :wrapperCol="wrapperCol"
        label="序号">
        <a-input-number v-decorator="[ 'iOrder', {}]" />
      </a-form-item>
      <a-form-item
        :labelCol="labelCol"
        :wrapperCol="wrapperCol"
        label="业务模块名称">
        <a-input placeholder="请输入业务模块名称" v-decorator="['sName', {}]" />
      </a-form-item>
      <a-form-item
        :labelCol="labelCol"
        :wrapperCol="wrapperCol"
        label="业务数据表">
        <a-input placeholder="请输入业务数据表" v-decorator="['sBusdataTable', {}]" />
      </a-form-item>

    </a-form>
  </a-spin>
  <a-button type="primary" @click="handleOk">确定</a-button>
  <a-button type="primary" @click="handleCancel">取消</a-button>
</a-drawer>
